Final Long-Term Reporting from a Randomized Controlled IDE Trial for Lumbar 
Artificial Discs in Single-Level Degenerative Disc Disease: 7-Year Results.

Radcliff K(1), Zigler J(2), Braxton E(3), Buttermann G(4), Coric D(5), Derman 
P(2), Garcia R(6), Jorgensen A(7), Ferko NC(8), Situ A(8), Yue J(9).

