Cost-effectiveness analysis of a school- and community-based intervention to 
promote a healthy lifestyle and prevent type 2 diabetes in vulnerable families 
across Europe: the Feel4Diabetes-study.

Willems R(1), Tsoutsoulopoulou K(2), Brondeel R(3), Cardon G(3), Makrilakis 
K(4), Liatis S(4), Lindström J(5), Kivelä J(5), González-Gil EM(6), 
Giménez-Legarre N(7), Usheva N(8), Iotova V(9), Tankova T(10), Antal E(11), 
